dialogue.text: You little orange noodle, I was only decieving you...
I'm the one that's supposed to decieve you, you know...
Shut it! I don't want to hear another WORD out of your stupid mo-
You're assuming I can actually talk?
OH MY GOSH JUST STOP ALREADY!
You're the one not stopping to get your weird fantasy of you with Liz together real...
OK, I HAD ENOUGH OF THAT!
